<h4 id="Article-145093">SpaMedica holds cake sale for Comic Relief</h4>
<div id="imageContentb96433b76dd4418b8b50a0ea9ce67b4a">
</div>
<p>SpaMedica Manchester held a cake sale on Friday 24<sup>th</sup> March to raise money for Comic Relief on Red Nose Day. </p>
<p>Our team put their baking skills to the test, whipping up an array of delicious cakes, including chocolate brownies, lemon and poppy seed cake and red velvet cupcakes. Other team members brought in chocolate cookies and cherry tarts. </p>
<p>The cakes were very popular with staff and patients alike, and we raised a fantastic £67.06 through donations, which SpaMedica has topped uo to £100. We hope this small gesture makes a big difference.</p>
<p> </p>
